<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">为响应习近平总书记在首届全民阅读大会致贺信中提倡阅读的讲话精神，优化校园阅读环境，推动书香校园建设，引导大学生与书为友，养成多读书、读好书、善读书的良好习惯，经济管理学院积极响应学校号召参加第六届江西省高校图书馆超星杯“一书一世界，共读不孤独”移动阅读活动，并在此次活动中取得了佳绩！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240508/1715148519916007882.png" title="1715148519916007882.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240511/1715427985662012769.png" title="1715427985662012769.png" alt="image.png" width="679" height="458" style="width: 679px; height: 458px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240508/1715148586056041652.png" title="1715148586056041652.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240508/1715148602263040282.png" title="1715148602263040282.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240508/1715148628928094096.png" title="1715148628928094096.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240508/1715148667616029617.png" title="1715148667616029617.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240508/1715148694042038779.png" title="1715148694042038779.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240508/1715148735866068565.png" title="1715148735866068565.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 244); font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240508/1715148758854049658.png" title="1715148758854049658.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">经管学子在此次活动中的卓越表现值得肯定，同时也要感谢学校对学生的大力支持！ 此次活动不仅营造了良好的读书文化范围，还培养了学生良好的阅读习惯，激发了学生的读书热情。希望同学们继续保持阅读习惯，以书为友，以读为乐！</span></p>